Text: TENN VNG capacity NovForwarded by Victoria VersenHOUECT on AM From Victoria Versen AM To Cindy CT Sabra L CT Jesse CT cc bcc Victoria VersenHOUECT Subject TENN VNG capacity Nov Here is your VNG capacity for November L L primary deliveries Cornwell S Webster Cobb SWebster SWebster Please let me know if you have any questions or problems with this Thanks Vicki

OctoberJanuary Parking deal TENN Cc I know that you have already set up the TAGG deals I just wanted to be sure that you had all of the information We are able to park up to over the month of October The gas is to be returned to us in January The fee is per MMBtu but it will be negotiable on a daily basis This will be billed prorata from October to January The volumes can also flluctuate daily Please let me know if you have any questions Vicki x

RE American Heart WalkThanks Chris Original Message From Germany Chris Sent Monday October PM To Versen Victoria Subject RE American Heart Walk Put me down for NOT PER MILE YOU CRAZY WOMAN Original Message From Versen Victoria Sent Monday October PM To Pereira Susan W Ring Andrea Ames Chuck Neal Scott Hodge John Smith Maureen Barbe Robin Pimenov Vladi Mckay Brad Mckay Jonathan Keavey Peter F Brawner Sandra F Taylor Craig Goodell Scott Savvas Leonidas Townsend Judy Germany Chris Bates Kimberly Lamadrid Victor Garcia Clarissa Gillespie Steve Sanchez Christina Wood Tracy Superty Robert Allwein Robert Boudreaux Shanna Collins Joann Homco Meredith Loocke Kelly Ordway Chris Arteaga Airam Carter Tamara Halstead Lia Prudenti Dan Ramirez Robert Saldana Alex Jackson Brandee Choate Heather Kelly Katherine L Villarreal Jesse Subject American Heart Walk Hello everyone My husband Ryan is going to be participating in the American Heart Walk on November He is walking on behalf of our daughter Sydney who was born in May of this year with Congenital Heart Disease If anyone would like to sponsor us with a cash donation we would be very appreciative I will be accepting donations today and tomorrow This is a wonderful organization whose research saves lives like Sydneys every day All donations are matched by Enron and are tax deductible Please help this worthwhile cause if you can Thanks Vicki Versen x

FW Ashland ChemicalsOriginal Message From McFatridge Thomas Sent Tuesday November AM To Versen Victoria Subject FW Ashland Chemicals Importance High FYI Original Message From McFatridge Thomas Sent Tuesday November AM To Rohauer Tanya Cc Baxter Bryce Valderrama Lisa Eubanks Jr David W Subject Ashland Chemicals Importance High Tanya This is a followup to my two calls this morning I have talked to Pat Ebert at Ashland I asked her why they refuse to pay their October invoices She said that her management wants to speak to someone in upper management at Enron I asked to speak to her manager and was told that she was in a meeting I asked her to get her out of the meeting She did not comply Her managers name is Sherry Tackett Her phone number is I left her a messsage I told her that I expect payment for the ENA upstream for and for ENA for I also told her she received to commodity so the payment is due I told her expect it today I left my phone number and told her to call me as soon as possible Thanks Tom McFatridge
